          # Module 5 — Aggregations & GROUP BY

## 📌 Learning Objectives

After completing this module, you should be able to:

- Use aggregate functions to summarize data.
- Group records using `GROUP BY`.
- Understand the difference between `WHERE` and `HAVING`.
- Generate subtotals using `ROLLUP`.
- Generate all subtotal combinations using `CUBE`.
- Create custom summaries using `GROUPING SETS`.
- Build business reports using aggregation techniques.

